---

# 💡 Simple Example (Mind Blowing)

## Without DOM:

```html
<p>0</p>
```

👉 Count kabhi change nahi hoga

---

## With DOM:

```js
let count = 0
button.onclick = () => {
  count++
  document.querySelector("p").innerText = count
}
```

👉 Now it becomes a **real app**

